'''約書亞·亞倫·菲格利'''（{{lang-en|Joshua Aaron Phegley}}，{{bd|1989年|2月12日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的捕手。他先前曾效力過白襪、運動家與小熊等隊。

==職業生涯==
===芝加哥白襪===
2013年7月5日，菲格利登上大聯盟。他在初登場便敲出大聯盟首安和首分打點。7月7日，菲格利在面對[[大衛·普萊斯|大衛·普萊斯]]敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite news|title=David Price throws 8-hit complete game as Rays sweep White Sox|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=330707130|work=ESPN|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=July 25, 2013|date=July 7, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111143/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=330707130|dead-url=no}}</ref>4天後，他敲出了生涯首發滿貫砲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://m.mlb.com/player/572033/josh-phegley/2013/gamelogs/R/hitting/MLB |title=Josh Phegley Stats, Fantasy & News | athletics.com |publisher=M.mlb.com |accessdate=2015-06-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614093537/http://m.mlb.com/player/572033/josh-phegley/2013/gamelogs/R/hitting/MLB |archivedate=2015-06-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他出賽65場比賽，打擊率為2成06。<ref>[http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/profile.asp?P=Josh-Phegley {{Wayback|url=http://www.thebaseballcube.com/players/profile.asp?P=Josh-Phegley |date=20170616135214 }} Josh Phegley Baseball Statistics [2007-2016]<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

2014年，他僅出賽11場比賽，打擊率為2成16，並敲出3轟與7分打點。<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://m.mlb.com/player/572033/josh-phegley |title=Josh Phegley Stats, Fantasy & News {{!}} MLB.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2018-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920130325/http://m.mlb.com/player/572033/josh-phegley |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===奧克蘭運動家===
2014年球季結束後，白襪隊將菲格利、[[馬可斯·塞米恩|馬可斯·塞米恩]]、[[克里斯·巴希特|克里斯·巴希特]]和Rangel Ravelo交易至運動家，換來Jeff Samardzija和Michael Ynoa。<ref>{{cite news|title=A's trade pitcher Jeff Samardzija to White Sox|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=12004608|accessdate=December 9, 2014|agency=Associated Press|publisher=ESPN.com|date=December 9, 2014}}</ref>

2015年9月中，菲格利在賽前練習時不小心被正在練習揮棒的隊友Billy Butler擊中頭部。<ref name=autogenerated1 /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.athleticsnation.com/2015/9/20/9359891/athletics-call-up-bryan-anderson-to-spell-concussed-josh-phegley |title=Oakland A's call up Bryan Anderson to spell concussed Josh Phegley - Athletics Nation<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317143706/http://www.athleticsnation.com/2015/9/20/9359891/athletics-call-up-bryan-anderson-to-spell-concussed-josh-phegley |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/150517176/athletics-josh-phegley-has-a-concussion/ |title=Athletics Josh Phegley has a concussion {{!}} MLB.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705132633/http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/150517176/athletics-josh-phegley-has-a-concussion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/athletics/article/A-s-pitching-probables-Sept-23-25-6522857.php |title=A’s Josh Phegley out for the season after concussion - SFGate<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2018-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617115836/https://www.sfgate.com/athletics/article/A-s-pitching-probables-Sept-23-25-6522857.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>這起意外使得他因為腦震盪必須提前結束球季。該年他出賽73場比賽，打擊率為2成49，並敲出9轟與34分打點。<ref name=autogenerated1 />

2016年球季，菲格利因為右膝得到滑膜炎，造成他該年僅出賽25場比賽。<ref name=autogenerated1 /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/188145548/josh-phegley-has-knee-surgery-to-remove-cyst/ |title=Josh Phegley has knee surgery to remove cyst {{!}} MLB.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317143037/http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/188145548/josh-phegley-has-knee-surgery-to-remove-cyst/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/athletics-josh-phegley-dealing-with-sore-knee/ |title=Athletics' Josh Phegley: Dealing with sore knee - CBSSports.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317054955/http://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/athletics-josh-phegley-dealing-with-sore-knee/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/8/27/12674220/oakland-as-catcher-josh-phegley-has-setback-with-knee |title=Oakland A's catcher Josh Phegley has setback with knee - Athletics Nation<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317233419/http://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/8/27/12674220/oakland-as-catcher-josh-phegley-has-setback-with-knee |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/198026136/as-josh-phegley-hospitalized-with-synovitis/ |title=A's Josh Phegley hospitalized with synovitis {{!}} MLB.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708203534/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/198026136/as-josh-phegley-hospitalized-with-synovitis/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他的打擊率為2成56，並敲出1轟與10分打點。而這年他的阻殺率只有11%。<ref name=autogenerated1 />

2019年5月7日，菲格利接捕了[[麥克·菲爾斯|麥克·菲爾斯]]的無安打比賽。這不僅是2019年第一場無安打，也是大聯盟史上第300場無安打比賽。該年12月2日，菲格利未獲得球團續約，於是他進入了自由球員市場。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sfchronicle.com/athletics/article/A-s-reportedly-deal-second-baseman-Jurickson-14876022.php|title=A’s part with 2018 All-Star Blake Treinen, trade Jurickson Profar|author=Susan Slusser|date=December 2, 2019|website=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]|accessdate=December 2, 2019|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921061928/https://www.sfchronicle.com/athletics/article/A-s-reportedly-deal-second-baseman-Jurickson-14876022.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===芝加哥小熊===
2020年1月17日，菲格利與小熊簽下小聯盟合約。他在8月30日被球隊放進指定讓渡名單內。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/08/cubs-to-acquire-jose-martinez.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-09-01 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105232829/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/08/cubs-to-acquire-jose-martinez.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過9月30日球隊執行菲格利的選擇權，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/09/cubs-select-josh-phegley-dfa-josh-osich.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-04 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027171005/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/09/cubs-select-josh-phegley-dfa-josh-osich.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後他在球季結束後成為自由球員。

2021年2月3日，菲格利宣布退休。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/02/josh-phegley-announces-retirement.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-04 |archive-date=2021-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215070758/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/02/josh-phegley-announces-retirement.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

